highlights.text: “Locked out of Heaven” by Bruno Mars is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Israel, up 67 spots at #93.
“יהיה טוב & מים שקופים” by Omer Adam and Jasmin Moallem is the highest new entry on Top Songs Israel at #72.
Eden Hason has the most spots on Top Songs Israel. “לאהוב אותך כל יום” is the highest at #3.
“לשוב הביתה” by Ishay Ribo has been on Top Songs Israel the longest, at 287 weeks straight.
